name: MENCRANG
description: a composition of the word "mencrang" which in Sundanese means sparkling. This work is a collaborative work that tells about a city that became history when my friend and I received art education. where the city is famous for its flower city, namely the city of "Bandung". One of the things that grabs attention is the extraordinary development of the fashion world in this city. This work is one of the artifacts about a journey of my work
